25
[p 
	"The purpose of this page is to document all the known tricks of the GBA Mega Man Zero games so far.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Because of the nature of this site, we concentrate here on tricks that are nearly impossible to perform in real play, but are useful in the making of tool-assisted speedruns. For most of the tricks, a 
	[a class=intlink href=/Glossary 
		"frame advance
	]a
	" feature in an emulator is a definite must-have.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Note: "Zero" on this page refers to the player character Zero, unless the context clearly indicates otherwise.
	$LF
]p
